                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Even mercenaries of great skill can find it hard to escape from harm should they accidentally enter a place most dangerous. Atiyah knows this quite well, and considers it strongly when recruiting new members. He has heard plenty of spin-chilling tales from those of the same walk of life as him, after all...",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(204, 191, 173)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Special Rule — Withering Corrosion: After your opponent uses a Skill, remove 1 Candle of Life point. Once 4 Candle of Life points are depleted, you lose the match.",
